name: Tramtop Gunslingers of the Swamp
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Tramtop Gunslingers of the Swamp were involved in the initial conception of the Thespin Skytram. Now a member of a group researching the intersection of Groodu and Rootmason magics, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
